Type RailOCS

# RailOCS (static, slot 0 only) for TP=4 (tors=4), full connectivity across rails:
# - Each rail (gpu_index) is one ToR, so tors = GpusPerServer = 4
# - OCS planes: 3 (enough to realize full mesh K4 via 3 matchings)
# - Connectivity does NOT reconfigure during the run in current implementation.

Servers 32
GpusPerServer 4
Planes 3

LinkSpeedGbps 400
LinkLatencyNs 800
SwitchLatencyNs 800

SlotUs 100
ReconfigUs 0

ScheduleFile /data/csg-htsim/sim/datacenter/topologies/rail_ocs_tp4_fullmesh_3p_400g.schedule


